  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Tegoprazan in ERD Patients With Nighttime Heartburn and Sleep Disturbance</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-blind, Randomized, Active-controlled Phase 4 (Pilot) Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Tegoprazan in ERD Patients With Nighttime Heartburn and Sleep Disturbance</official_title>
